name: Chattee
overview: Chattee is made for you. It is the future way to communicate through real voice with everybody who is interested to chat by live-voice. It’s a new way to interact trough social networks.It makes easier to the world to be connected. It is completely free, does not matter if you talk to one person or with several, neither if you have access to a computer nor smartphone, works with any phone and from any part of the world where there is an access number. Chattee was founded by Ricardo Gonda, an entrepreneur who has dedicated his life to develop telecom companies across the world. Leonardo Eugenio, an entrepreneur specialized in multimedia marketing in Brazil and Jose Gregorio Garcia also an entrepreneur with experience in finance an international business. This is the creator management team of Chattee.
